name: Origami sUSDS + Sky Farms
reason:
[sUSDS+s](https://origami.finance/collections/sky-collection/1-0x0f90a6962e86b5587b4c11bA2B9697dC3bA84800/info) is an ERC4626 vault created by [Origami Finance](https://x.com/origami_fi) with a deposit/withdrawal asset of USDS. There are no restrictions on depositing/exiting in the vault, so the liquidity is unlimited and slippage free.

This is an auto-compounding vault which actually uses programmatic CoW swap orders to swap harvested SKY / SPK rewards back into the USDS vault assets.

It is the asset which backs TempleDAOs treasury and been live for coming up to 12 months.

Barter have recently whitelisted this asset into their solver.
